		<br />
		<a href="mailto:{{devs}}"><button class="button lightorange">rock out</button></a>
		<br /><br /><br /><br />
	</div>


	<div class="two-col">
		<h4>Apply to intern for us in LA</h4>
		<p> Looking for a "Jack-of-all-trades" to help us out in all aspects of our business. We're growing at an unbelievable rate, and we want someone interested in getting experience in every department of a growing food delivery company. You'll learn your way around and become an integral part of our operations!</p>
		<br />
		<a href="mailto:{{recruiting}}"><button class="button lightorange">apply now</button></a>
		<br /><br /><br /><br />
	</div>

	<div class="two-col">
		<div>
			<h4>Who are you?!</h4>
			<p>We're people! People who love food so much that we want to share our passion without asking you to even leave your homes.</p>
			<br>
			<button class="button green" ng-click="navigation.link('/about','push')">Meet the team</button>
			<br /><br /><br /><br />
		</div>
	</div>


</div>


